bool DTrackSDK::isLocalDataPortValid (  ) 

Is UDP socket open to receive tracking data on local machine? An open socket is needed to receive data, but does not guarantee this.

Especially in case no data is sent to this port.

Replaces valid() in older SDKs.

Returns:
socket open?
